    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        "To provide us with more practical insights, we have computer labs, practical sessions, and practical exams.",
        "Qualifications for each scholarship may vary; you have to check which one is good for you.",
        "The placement cell working in our college will arrange numerous opportunities to build our career. They will provide training sessions to attend interviews. Additionally, we can utilize the library facility, which is one of the best in the university, for interview preparation.",
        "There are a lot of scholarships provided by the college as well as the government to college students. Scholarships are available for minority students, students who have opted for Hindi, the best student within the department, the best student in the college, handicapped students, etc.",
        "The college is well known for its volleyball team, which is one of the best teams in Kerala.",
        "The hostel is situated within the campus itself, making it convenient for students who stay in the hostel. The warden of the hostel is a priest.",
        "St. Thomas College, Palai is a pioneering institute in Kottayam that upholds its name for sports and excellent education."
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        "Placement is a little disappointing since not many companies come here, but still, some banks come for recruitment, offering jobs.",
        "The college has a system that helps poor students, but to my knowledge, there are no loan facilities or scholarships provided by the college.",
        "As I already mentioned, it is a terrible college. It doesnt conduct any intercollege activities like sports, laboratory events, and such. However, it usually conducts workshops by various tech giants.",
        "St. Thomas College, Pala, has a hostel named Christhuraj. This college is typically old, and the hostel facilities are also of poor quality. The food and accommodation provided are extremely bad, with cheap facilities"
      ]
    },
